Title: An Act Changing the Name of Nagsangalan Elementary School in Barangay Talogtog, Municipality of Dolores, Province of Abra, to Don Rosalio Eduarte Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 326
An Act Changing the Name of Nagsangalan Elementary School in Barangay Talogtog, Municipality of Dolores, Province of Abra, to Don Rosalio Eduarte Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Nagsangalan Elementary School in Barangay Talogtog, Municipality of Dolores, Province of Abra, is changed to Don Rosalio Eduarte Elementary School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
